 众所周知，docker作为新欣容器技术解决方案，解决了应用环境多变，开发、测试以及线上环境的不一致而导致的诸多问题，使用docker可以一次封装，到处运行，只需要在开发环节封装好容器镜像后，在测试环境和线上环境就能保障运行环境一致。而为了把复杂的业务拆分为多个子业务单元，使应用程序之间实现业务解耦，降低业务复杂度，所以出现了所谓“微服务”的概念，所谓“微服务”，就是尽可能让一个应用做更少的事，多个应用组合来实现业务逻辑，'),(1318,317,'keywords_value',''),(1340,319,'description_value',''),(1341,319,'keywords_value',''),(1342,319,'_edit_lock','1535292256:1'),(1343,319,'_edit_last','1'),(1282,309,'description_value',''),(1283,309,'keywords_value',''),(1284,313,'_wp_page_template','account/findpassword.php'),(1285,314,'description_value',''),(1286,314,'keywords_value',''),(1287,314,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(1288,314,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1289,314,'_menu_item_object_id','313'),(1290,314,'_menu_item_object','page'),(1291,314,'_menu_item_target',''),(1292,314,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1293,314,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(1294,314,'_menu_item_url',''),(1295,315,'description_value',''),(1296,315,'keywords_value',''),(1297,315,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(1298,315,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1299,315,'_menu_item_object_id','313'),(1300,315,'_menu_item_object','page'),(1301,315,'_menu_item_target',''),(1302,315,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1303,315,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(1304,315,'_menu_item_url',''),(1344,320,'description_value',''),(1345,320,'keywords_value',''),(1317,317,'description_value','        前文介绍了k8s是什么，并谈到k8s会对主机节点进行资源再次抽象，接下来再来详细了解下k8s是如何工作的，以及k8s各个资源是如何协同配合的。\r'),(1315,313,'description_value',''),(1316,313,'keywords_value',''),(1336,317,'views','7'),(1346,320,'_edit_lock','1535374578:1'),(1347,320,'_edit_last','1'),(1349,320,'views','50'),(1350,319,'_wp_trash_meta_status','draft'),(1351,319,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1535292411'),(1352,319,'_wp_desired_post_slug',''),(1354,321,'description_value',''),(1355,321,'keywords_value',''),(1356,321,'_edit_lock','1535421777:1'),(1357,322,'description_value','趣闻-java的来历：\r'),(1358,322,'keywords_value',''),(1359,321,'_edit_last','1'),(1360,322,'_wp_attached_file','2018/08/mpops